name: Patrick Gonzales
description: Well, i am Patrick Gonzales by real name. I was born on 25th of july, 1964 (52 years ). I am 5 feet 9 tall in height, have a black hair and black eyes. I`m a Latin American/Hispanic by ethnic. I was born in Yucatan Penninsula Quintana Roo, Bacalar, Mexico but raised/grew up in Monetery, California before i got deployed here in Lagos mainland for keeping the mission safe . I`m the only child that my parents gave birth to. I have been brought-up in a very discipline atmosphere where values and principles have always been given priority
